------------------------------------
BILDAD: A Very Simple Billiards Game
------------------------------------

Disclaimer: This program is by no means complete, not even Beta. Run it with
your own risk.

Requirements
------------

ansi C compiler
make
X server
xlib
opengl
glx

How to play
-----------

adjust cue direction:   w, x, a, d
change hitting point:   i
hit:                    Enter

-* This game have no rules, will update soon :-)
